                                Not everyone has the luxury of a large backyard, but that doesn’t mean you can’t have a thriving garden. Even the smallest outdoor space can be transformed into a lush, green oasis with the right approach. Whether you're working with a small balcony, a compact patio, or just a tiny corner of your yard, there are countless ways to create a beautiful and functional garden.
