                            </ul>
    
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Embrace Container Gardening for Flexibility</h2>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Container gardening allows you to control soil quality and drainage perfectly. Containers can be moved to follow the sun or brought indoors during harsh weather.</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
